appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
* Mobile application now stores and saves your phone number.
* Added automatic refresh when you first login and each time you reopen.
* Added manual Refresh button to the top of the Assigned Shipments screen.
* Added a warning if you attempt to track more than one shipment.
* When Completing/Transferring, automatically navigate you back to Assigned Shipments.
* Reduced the size of the header.
* Resolved various bugs and issues, updated translations.
* Minor UI/UX changes.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
This release includes major changes of stop detection analysis with tracking banner on android and IOS devices.
It also includes bug fixes on tracking activity, now we can track android device with 5 minutes interval and IOS device with 1000mt. of travelling.
Some other fixes:
-> Battery performance tracking
-> Automatic remove shipment on marking complete and transfer
-> Translations for all popups in supporting languages.
